(2229, 'Cefdin 300mg 10 caps.', 'سيفدين 300مجم 10 كبسولات', '', '63', 'Cefdinir', 'Novartis', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Antibiotic.cephalosporin.third-generation', '300mg', 'Cefdinir is indicated to treat acute bacterial otitis media, acute maxillary sinusitis, community-acquired (CA) pneumonia, acute bacterial exacerbations of chronic bronchitis, pharyngitis/tonsillitis, and uncomplicated skin and skin structure infections in children and adults.[L7330,A180739]
